Repository includes my settings and custom scripts.

1. The rule change access permissions for /dev/tty* devices
   and notify their connecting and disconnecting.
file: nix/etc/udev/rules.d/60-tty.rules
file: nix/usr/local/scripts/notify-send_custom.sh

2. Astyle config:
--style=bsd --add-brackets --indent-switches --pad-header --unpad-paren --pad-oper --align-pointer=name
